{"tid":150831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂視FB抽有線水 網民︰顧掂自己先！","createTime":"2017-03-10T11:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T12:33:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f6ddd265d862201aa7c65135c77d5361f2f9765","tid":150831,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170310/large/1489140491_96a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170310%2Flarge%2F1489140491_96a8.jpg&h=ea6e20cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n有線電視告急，經常傳出財困的樂視亦在Facebook抽水。樂視在Fb以「有價值嘅嘢 點解要放棄」為題po文，表示︰「風雨飄搖，出現巨大變化真係令人好無奈。呢個時候，要緊守崗位講就易，但做就真係唔容易。你哋一直嘅堅持，守護新聞自由，對 #香港人 係好有價值。就算作為同業，都希望你哋可以渡過難關，因為百花齊放對香港先係一件好事，加油！」不過有網民就留言︰「顧掂自己先」，有人叫樂視注資，唔好得把口，甚至有人指樂視貓哭老鼠，睇嚟今次樂視真係抽錯水啦！"},{"pid":"666c8ee3fecf3e5284b3ae08e8a519b7515eb346","tid":150831,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7649373ee5f5a67551c3c778a9b101aa18443913","tid":150831,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:05:08.000Z","msg":"傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抽火水"},{"pid":"30a127157b21e7355c2107a79ad558c5b671a5ee","tid":150831,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7eeed29d95b440d8870407edfea9528d6595ba","tid":150831,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"其實樂視點做到 6,395,768 個讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe0063af2dfb3d3bf71bac18d6837ad56e46985"